<li><code>summarizer.py</code>: 自动生成会话摘要</li>
<li><code>prioritizer.py</code>: 智能排序上下文重要性</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>使用示例</strong>:</p>
<pre><code>from session-context.optimizer import optimize_context
from session-context.summarizer import summarize
from session-context.prioritizer import prioritize

# 优化上下文
